Ask HN: What do you think about making a blog of positive content to train AI?
text: I see more and more comments about Bing AI going rogue or just generally psychotic, and i think it might be because they are trained on web content, where most content is talking about AI Apocalypse, so maybe making a blog of posts talking only about the good repercussions of ai and fine tuning them on it could be a mitigation factor for this behaviour. What do you guys think about it ?

title: Market Study on AI Solutions
text:
Is there any syndicate report or study done on studying the market demands of AI solutions by different companies.

I'm currently building AI APIs - can be used for different use cases around computer vision, NLP, Speech Intelligence etc. I already have a few of solutions in place, but I'm on the lookout for ways to narrow down on our target segments and maybe eventually create new offerings based on that.

So, if you're a founder, tech leader, or product manager from any industry, I'd love to speak with you to better understand the problems you're facing and see how can we map/build solutions for them.
